Package level2Assignment1

Class Address

java.lang.Object
level2Assignment1.Address
public class Address extends Object
Represents a physical address, including details such as street, number, city, country, and postal code. This class is designed to encapsulate all necessary information for an address and provide methods to access and modify these details.
